      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "openEuler Base-service SIG 是什么？",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "openEuler Base-service SIG（Special Interest Group，特别兴趣小组）负责 The Base-service team is responsible for maintain the basic package for linux.。该 SIG 共有 44 名核心成员，维护 533 个代码仓库，属于 基础设施与工具 领域。"
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "如何参与 openEuler Base-service SIG？",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "参与 openEuler Base-service SIG 的方式：1）向相关仓库（如 openeuler/re2-rust、src-openeuler/re2-rust、openeuler/unizip）提交 Pull Request；2）订阅邮件列表 dev@openeuler.org；3）参加 SIG 定期工作会议，会议信息见 openEuler 官网活动日历。"
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "openEuler Base-service SIG 包含哪些代码仓库？",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "openEuler Base-service SIG 共维护 533 个代码仓库，主要包括：openeuler/re2-rust、src-openeuler/re2-rust、openeuler/unizip 等。完整列表见 https://www.openeuler.org/zh/sig/Base-service。"
        }
      },
